118
00:05:55,393 --> 00:05:58,714
moment when apparent chaos becomes perfect order in your mind.

119
00:05:58,714 --> 00:06:03,095
It's just a different way of thinking and related to that is racing games.

120
00:06:03,095 --> 00:06:05,955
You can even like Rez or Thumper or the Wipeout series.

